{"tid":2343894,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 警員到達深水埗主教山減壓缸清拆現場 ，工人圍封警告勿進入　","createTime":"2020-12-28T09:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T09:33:43.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a0353b6c5767ef955ddf8d875f1aad7824b08e","tid":2343894,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/133014984_3765085843577008_2043797111076819020_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=6UW5W0s2WJoAX8R6wpe&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=5b902b823d50dbe457ebefd5bc2e1007&amp;oe=600FBC80\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F133014984_3765085843577008_2043797111076819020_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D6UW5W0s2WJoAX8R6wpe%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D5b902b823d50dbe457ebefd5bc2e1007%26oe%3D600FBC80&h=2cafc031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深水埗主教山減壓缸清拆 市民到場拍照<br />\n下午工人圍封警告勿進入 警員到場<br />\n深水埗主教山上的食水減壓缸因有結構危險，近日清拆，內部結構曝光。減壓缸以巨型石柱支撐，有紅磚砌成拱門，甚具特色，被形容為「古羅馬式建築」，吸引不少市民到場拍照留念。<br />\n。<br />\n不過，下午近三時，有工人圍封該處，市民已不能入內。鐵絲網上掛出告示，指該處為工地範圍，非請勿進，違者報警處理」。其後有兩名警員到場，又曾進入地盤。"},{"pid":"c6bc01041a39cf825d7207f0e691db4c137b95db","tid":2343894,"uid":58948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:31:25.000Z","msg":"標題黨"},{"pid":"3650ed4eb4d27c05646cfdb0bc50096438e66fbc","tid":2343894,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"同當年大帽山結冰都堅持上山既人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}